          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "usp_BudgetFacilitySurvey_GetFilteredSBMRList",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve a filtered list of SBMR (Survey Budget Management Report) records from the database. It performs a query on the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "SBMR.SBMRHeader",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " table, joining it with the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "SBMR.SbmrAction",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " table to include descriptive information about the SBMR action. The procedure filters records based on the provided SBMR reference number, agency division sequence ID, and optionally, a facility sequence ID."
        }
      ]
